</blockquote><s>How the fuck "equipment" = "industrial tools"? <img src="https://forums.sufficientvelocity.com/styles/sv_smiles/xenforo/FacePalm2.png" class="smilie" loading="lazy" alt=":facepalm:" title="Facepalm    :facepalm:" data-shortname=":facepalm:"> ...</s><br>
