</blockquote>Isn't the Privacy Curtain and everything in it totally invisible to precogs? Also he can't use SSS tech offensively against Endbringers, unless Polymorph Cockroach works on Behemoth and he uses a SSS Roomba to get rid of pests. Even that might be stretching it. The Curtain works because privacy is a household issue. It prevents almost <i>anything </i>from viewing the Workshop in any way.</div>
				
