					<div class="bbWrapper"><blockquote data-attributes="member: 42519" data-quote="Koraan" data-source="post: 20556832" class="bbCodeBlock bbCodeBlock--expandable bbCodeBlock--quote js-expandWatch is-expandable">
	
		<div class="bbCodeBlock-title">

			
				<a href="https://forums.sufficientvelocity.com/threads/brocktons-celestial-forge-worm-jumpchain.70036/page-649#post-20556832" class="bbCodeBlock-sourceJump" rel="nofollow" data-xf-click="attribution" data-content-selector="#post-20556832">Koraan said:</a>
			
