		<article class="message-body js-selectToQuote">
			
				
			

			<div itemprop="text">
				
					<div class="bbWrapper"><blockquote data-attributes="member: 60476" data-quote="The Shallow" data-source="post: 20558188" class="bbCodeBlock bbCodeBlock--expandable bbCodeBlock--quote js-expandWatch">
	
		<div class="bbCodeBlock-title">

			
				<a href="https://forums.sufficientvelocity.com/threads/brocktons-celestial-forge-worm-jumpchain.70036/page-649#post-20558188" class="bbCodeBlock-sourceJump" rel="nofollow" data-xf-click="attribution" data-content-selector="#post-20558188">The Shallow said:</a>
			
		</div>
	
	<div class="bbCodeBlock-content">
		
		<div class="bbCodeBlock-expandContent js-expandContent ">
			Sting Gems would be WMDs, essentially. He could've wiped out the ABB, wiped out the Endbringers, bring enough of them and deal with Scion.
		</div>
		<div class="bbCodeBlock-expandLink js-expandLink"><a role="button" tabindex="0">Click to expand...</a></div>

<div class="bbCodeBlock-shrinkLink"><a>Click to shrink...</a></div>
	</div>
</blockquote>Heh. Nah. That's easier, quickier and smarter than just throwing grenades (even peally advanced) at Zion's avatar.<br>
