</blockquote>I believe Lord's way of going about the Warp Grenade and the dangers therein has less to do with Warp entities, regardless of shape or size, and more to do with the Warp Grenade being a persistent, mobile, unstable rift in reality, that can distort space-time around it.  Lord doesn't seem to be too keen on diverting away from the main Worm plot by adding the baddies of other series into the mix.<br>
<br>
And yeah, no killing EBs, cause then more will come.</div>
				
